data.description: Country atmosphere but just a short distance to all the amenities that Poulsbo has to offer. This home is a two bedroom with two ensuites with separate tub and shower enclosures. An efficient, open kitchen design with a skylight. This home features 2271 square feet of space with a family and living room. Free standing propane stove for efficient heat and aesthetic comfort. Attached to the home is a three car garage on a poured slab. The shop is a 4 bay shop with three doors and is plumbed with compressed air throughout the whole shop. Tall bays will accommodate a lift. Plenty of parking with 7 covered parking bays on the property. Fruit trees and ornamentals enhance the landscape with full fence area. This home is a must see!
